Description: Barely escaping the Human Unification Army, Lafiel and Jinto crash-land on Planet Clasbul, which is already under enemy occupation. With no means to rejoin the fleet, they must find a way to survive until rescued. However, the Abh princess is nothing more that a clueless girl, and Jinto must use his experience to protect her..
